[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "撮影、お疲れさまでしたー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00855",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "みんな",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "お疲れさまでしたー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00856",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "お疲れさまでしたー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00857",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "お疲れさまでしたー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00858",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "お疲れさまでした",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00859",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "お疲れさまでした",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00860",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "いやあ、どちらもいい企画になりましたな！\nこのたびは本当に感謝いたしまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00861",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ううん、こちらこそ！\n本物のアイドルは、やっぱりすごかったです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00862",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "それにしても、よくコラボしようなんて思ったわよね。\nカウントダウンフェスのライバルなのに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00863",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "それはキューンが、『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』の\nファンだから……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00864",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "わああ！？　やめてよ、恥ずかしい……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00865",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "そういうことでしたか。\nやっと腑に落ちたでござるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00866",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "なに？　どういうこと？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00867",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "初めてバズった我々の動画。どういう人が\n拡散してくれているのか、調べたのでありまするが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00868",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "一番最初に拡散してくれていたのは、\nなんとキューン殿だったことに気付きまして",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00869",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "えっ！　嘘、なんで？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00870",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "……それは、我々の活動コンセプトに由来している",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00871",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "私たちはね。「楽しいことがやりたい」\n「その『楽しい』を見ている人に共有したい」",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00872",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "そういう想いを込めて、活動してるんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00873",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "初めて皆さんの動画を見た時……すっごく楽しかった。\n他のみんなにも見てほしいと思ったんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00874",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "本当に、それだけなの。このコラボだって、\n皆さんと一緒にやったら、きっと楽しいだろうなって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00875",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "皆さんは、ライバルだけど……\n同時に私、皆さんのファンになっちゃったみたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00876",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "そうだったんだ……嬉しいなあ、\n『ＱＥジーンズ』にそう言ってもらえるなんて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00877",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "それに、アタシの夢と一緒で驚いちゃった。\nそういう意味じゃ、アタシたち仲間なのかもね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00878",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "おお……同志。つまり、ベップもアイドルだった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00879",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "自己認識の歪曲を確認。マジレスを推奨",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00880",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "そうは言っても！　手加減なんてしないから！\nフェスの枠は私たちがいただくわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00881",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "望むところ。\nどちらが勝っても恨みっこなし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00882",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "こっちも審査の日まで全力で頑張るよ。\nだから、そっちも頑張って！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00883",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "うん！　結果発表の日が楽しみだね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00884",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]